<section name="main:whatis">
<title><en>What is OCaml-R ?</en></title>
<p>
<en>OCaml-R provides OCaml bindings to the R math library and the R
library usable to embed R in your application.
</en>
</p>
<p>
<en>OCaml-R is still in development. Most of the
R math library functions are available. With the embedded R, it is
already possible to create variables and exchange basic data
between embedded R and OCaml sides.
</en>
</p>
